FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779296759
OL,3,CFuel duty increase to be scrapped,
OL,4,Csays Starmer
OL,6,FSteve Gooding, director of motoring
OL,7,Fresearch charity the RAC Foundation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Although today's news on fuel
OL,9,Fduty won't have the immediate effect
OL,10,Fof bringing forecourt prices down, at
OL,11,Fleast it shows that ministers have
OL,12,Fregistered the financial pain caused
OL,13,Fby rampant pump prices for individuals
OL,14,Fand for business.
OL,16,F"Since the start of the Iran conflict
OL,17,Fdrivers have already paid a war
OL,18,Fpremium of a staggering #3 billion in
OL,19,Finflated fuel prices, half a billion
OL,20,Fof which has gone to the Exchequer in
OL,21,FVAT receipts."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
